A combination of one of our longest-running and most popular styles and one of our most-loved older pieces, the Bow Runch creates a minimal coverage, flattering bottom with super-cute detailing, providing a perfect fit for all Moana Babes. Cheeky, yet tasteful, once you’ve rocked a runch, it’s hard to go back to anything else! Seamless and matching multiple separate tops of varying style and coverage, this is a must-have piece.

Prints may vary. Please note this piece reverses in to the same print design.  

  • Minimal coverage bottom
  • Runch detailing at rear
  • Bow, tie-up detailing
  • Italian lycra
  • Seamless and reversible
  • Please note; prints may vary slightly

Made and designed by Moana Bikini for the carefree, active girl.

Print designs are © Moana Lifestyle Pty Ltd

title: BOUNCING BURRITO
body_html:
﻿Allowing for more comfort and support, especially for the bustier Moana girl, this bra-style top not only features an eye-catching, vibrant print, but also includes underwire for an added secure feel. This top also includes an adjustable, tie-up back to help cater for all styles and sizes. This suit is complemented with reversible bottoms so you have the option to transform from one stunning look to another.

Sets cannot be broken up. Prints may vary. This top does not come with padding.

  • Two bikinis in one!
  • Supportive, bra-style top
  • Adjustable tie-up back
  • Cheeky booty coverage
  • Reversible bottom
  • Italian lycra
  • Please note; prints may vary slightly

Made and designed by Moana Bikini for the carefree, active girl.

Print designs are © Moana Lifestyle Pty Ltd

title: BOSS CHOKER
body_html: You asked and we delivered! Finally, our Campaign Model’s jewellery is available for you! This piece is strong, bold choker to both make a statement and accentuate your Moana Bikinis. Sitting high on your neck and featuring a Moana branded clasp, this will be a favourite, show-stopping piece with any outfit… but especially your Moana Bikinis!

body_html:

Available in two amazing, yet contrasting prints, this top matches multiple separate bottoms, providing a multitude of stunning, eye-catching sets.
